::Soundwave shrugs::
Soundwave: I do not know for sure, but I am guessing that we will try to 
spread this peace all the way to Cybertron.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------
::Gigatron hears Defection's orders and flys to his position::
Gigatron: Defection, what are we doing?
::He realizes that in not such a long time they went from being newcomers to 
Maximal allys.  Interesting how things change::

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------------------::The Neocons have settled into 
their new base, the Deathcon and are planning to strike where it hurts::
Megastorm: It would be best to attack the Predacons, who have splintered.
Galvatron: Your an idiot.  Vulois is the obvious place to strike.  He wants 
peace so much that he wont fight with the violence of a true warrior.  We 
shall make him our target.  But fine, if you want to attack the Predacons, 
you can do it alone.
::Jetstorm sniggers, getting the idea.  Megastorm isn't sure if he won or 
lost this one::
